### ========== USER REGISTRATION & AUTH ==========

### Register a new user (Role: User)
POST {{JWTAuthAPI_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123"
}

###

### Register an Admin (Role: Admin)
POST {{JWTAuthAPI_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register-admin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "AdminPass123"
}

###

### Login as User
POST {{JWTAuthAPI_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "SecurePass123"
}

###

### Login as Admin
POST {{JWTAuthAPI_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "AdminPass123"
}

###

### Refresh Token
POST {{JWTAuthAPI_HostAddress}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

###

### Logout
POST {{JWTAuthAPI_HostAddress}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

###

### ========== USER MANAGEMENT (ADMIN ONLY) ==========

### Get All Users (Admin Only)
GET {{JWTAuthAPI_HostAddress}}/api/usermanagement/users
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}

###

### Get User By ID (Admin Only)
GET {{JWTAuthAPI_HostAddress}}/api/usermanagement/users/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}

###

### Get My Profile (Any Authenticated User)
GET {{JWTAuthAPI_HostAddress}}/api/usermanagement/profile
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Change Password (Any Authenticated User)
PUT {{JWTAuthAPI_HostAddress}}/api/usermanagement/change-password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "currentPassword": "SecurePass123",
  "newPassword": "NewSecurePass456",
  "confirmPassword": "NewSecurePass456"
}

###

### Update User Role (Admin Only)
PUT {{JWTAuthAPI_HostAddress}}/api/usermanagement/users/2/role
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}

{
  "role": "Admin"
}

###

### Deactivate User (Admin Only)
PUT {{JWTAuthAPI_HostAddress}}/api/usermanagement/users/2/deactivate
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}

###

### Activate User (Admin Only)
PUT {{JWTAuthAPI_HostAddress}}/api/usermanagement/users/2/activate
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}

###

### Delete User (Admin Only)
DELETE {{JWTAuthAPI_HostAddress}}/api/usermanagement/users/2
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}

###
